(31516, 396, 396, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'With Whitemane gone for good, the Scarlet Crusade is finished. It\'s just a matter of sweeping up the refuse.$B$BThank you, $p. Not just for myself, but for everyone opposed to mindless hatred and bigotry.$B$BAnd, thank you for these two new blades. Anointed anew in her blood, they should serve me well as I take the fight to Scholomance and deal with Darkmaster Gandling.$B$BI bid you adieu for now.', 43345), -- Unto Dust Thou Shalt Return
(31515, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<The second anointed blade floats just in front of the wet statue. Steam rises from the sword.>$B$B<You get the uncanny feeling that the Hand of Providence has been waiting for you.>', 43345), -- Blades of the Anointed
